Class SuppressedChat

java.lang.Object
mb.pso.issuesystem.entity.im.SuppressedChat
@Entity public class SuppressedChat extends Object
Represents the suppression status of a chat for a specific employee.

Tracks whether a chat is suppressed for notifications.
